gomodel:SYNGO_568  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Endogenous and over-expression of WASF3 (WAVE3) localise in dendritic spines and protrusions in primary hippocampal cultures (11-14DIV).. Experimental description: 30/8/2017 Pim\n- Species of the cultured neurons is not mentioned in the paper.\n- Overexpressed protein were of mouse origin: \"Mouse brain was used to prepare cDNA from which WAVE1, WAVE3, and Nck1, were cloned\"" ;
